<note n="2" xml:id="n-2" target="#note-t-2">
<ab>
  <bibleref xmlns="http://www.vangoghletters.org/ns/" book="John" chap="11" v="35">John 11:35</bibleref>.</ab></note>
<note n="3" xml:id="n-3" target="#note-t-3">
  <ab>Regarding <rs type="lit" key="40"><hi rend="ital">Etude sur George Michel</hi></rs> by <rs type="pers" key="737">Alfred Sensier</rs>, <ref target="let044.xml#n-2">see letter 44, n. 2.</ref></ab></note>
<note n="4" xml:id="n-4" target="#note-t-4">
<ab>On <rs type="pers" key="1295">Rembrandt</rs>’s <rs type="ill" key="1735"><hi rend="ital">The pilgrims at Emmaus</hi></rs>, <ref target="let042.xml#n-9">see letter 42, n. 9.</ref></ab></note>
<note n="5" xml:id="n-5" target="#note-t-5">
<ab>Regarding this birthday, <ref target="let041.xml#n-9">see letter 41, n. 9.</ref></ab></note></div></body></text></TEI>
